Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uprisings are breaking out all over Sistina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What good will it do\Nfor the people to make a commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They all fear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, a single spark of revolt is all it takes.\NIt could very well burst into flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The impact of someone calling himself Cornaro\Nand slaying a Rossini is undeniably huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, more supporters of Theo Cornaro\Nhave been assembling in Marza.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A ragtag bunch of bottom-feeders like that.\NI'll be glad to crush them myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me leave right now!\NI'll be the one to avenge Salvador!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, they won't stop at Marza.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The people in neighboring towns\Nwill probably join the revolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would be wiser to leave\Nafter you've gathered sufficient troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so nonchalant?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, Juzel is right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dorni, gather 3,000,\Nno, make that 5,000 soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Five thousand?\NYou don't have confidence in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salvador only took a few hundred men,\Nand because of that, he perished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to lose you, too,\Nwhat will become of the Rossini family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never end up like—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to take any chance\Nof becoming a father who's lost two sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving as soon as I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is suppression really the only way\Nto deal with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to be saying such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our family forced our subjects into submission,\Nand eliminated anyone who rebelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we've always ruled this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to ease our grip now,\Nwe would only be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we have the Omerta flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain that Dorni\Nwill get revenge for Salvador.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theo Cornaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll make you pay\Nfor this crime with your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anywhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I go to the Rossini house,\NSalvador is not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were indeed a favorite of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salvador. He was such a fine man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was passionate, and had a lust\Nfor all kinds of pleasures,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and never asked any questions about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why aren't you heading back to the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because Salvador ordered me to kill\Nthe chamberlain who's accompanying Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I haven't fulfilled that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what they call the Way of the Assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sooner or later, Phederico\Nwill be sending his forces to defeat Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the battle draws near, both Theo Cornaro\Nand his mage will have their hands tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I intend to lure him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Can you beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I don't know. For one thing,\Nhe has those werewolf kids with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Werewolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Those twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, could they be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you like me to wrest those two\Naway from that chamberlain for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can!\NThose two will definitely be coming after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill the werewolves,\Nand you'll kill the chamberlain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When that's done,\NI want you to kill Theo and Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is like vengeance for Salvador?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That will be part of it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I've always had a hatred for those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking at them,\Nyou can tell that they trust each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me vomit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looking good! Louder, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A good number of soldiers have shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It feels totally different\Nthan before we fought Salvador.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting the sense that everyone's hearts\Nare being moved, more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'd like to build a castle right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A small one will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how high my court rank may be\Nby then, I would want to rule this village myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To make that happen, we need to bring an end\Nto the fighting on the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And before we do that,\Nwe must overthrow the Rossinis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The forces led by Dorni Rossini have left,\Nand are on their way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as we thought, they're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't turn this village into a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's counter them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Witch who murdered Mother\Nis nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me,\Nbut we have a personal matter to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We three will be away for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Whatever you do, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong with Irvin and the twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They went to eliminate some elements\Nthat might thwart us in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe the man in the center is Dorni Rossini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After losing Salvador, if he should lose Dorni next,\Nthe Rossini's iron rule should begin to crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the Rossini family rules,\Nwe'll be plundered, and killed for no good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other domain but Sistina\Nbeing governed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we all rose up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll overcome fear with courage,\Nand find hope in the depths of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's win this battle, and bring an end\Nto the Rossini family's tyranny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of those we love,\Nand for those we must protect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How impudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how sizable your forces may be,\Nthey're still just a ragtag crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll annihilate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rossini soldiers, now's the time\Nto pledge fealty with your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will eliminate everyone\Nwho might get in my master's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill you, and then I will also\Nkill Theo Cornaro and your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a Black Witch special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were those two pups\Nfrom that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A demon's barrier\Ncan't just be easily broken, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let the festivities begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Will you only defend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever is the last man standing wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were coating your weapon with my poison\Nwhile deflecting my blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamberlains must accomplish\Nmultiple tasks simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we also must think several steps ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Flames of Darkness are quite effective, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only a matter of time\Nbefore you can't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And while you're immobile,\Nthat demon will have its way with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rip you to shreds before that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll avenge Mother no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a wall surrounding the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try that move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We were so close, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:12:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why won't you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Dorni!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will fight by your side\Nuntil the end, Sir Dorni!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Irvin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Irvin! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Irvin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He is not destined to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Irvin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn them. I'll tear them apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take at least one of them down with me,\Nand tear them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Dorni...\NI have fulfilled my loyalty oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard.\NSo you were waiting for me to get fatigued?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way that I know how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So damned insolent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to bury this man\Nin the same way as the other casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I also want you\Nto call on the Rossini forces to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Comet, O Comet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you grant me my wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that star is a bad omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It will bring death and disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Theo Cornaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wail with grief, Witch of Eramu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting Star, Shooting Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My wish will surely be granted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aishela! Take her into custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After lasting for generations, the Rossini family's rule\Nended in a flash once it began to crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theo Cornaro's forces will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then we'll have to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As Lord of Sistina, I'm prepared\Nto fulfill my final task.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have to escape this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care where. I'm begging you to flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to lose you, too, I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Theo Cornaro if he'll negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to convince him\Nthat I'd be beneficial to his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a chance on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clear the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Get the Rossini family out!\N- Here comes the hero, Theo Cornaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo Cornaro, my name is Juzel Rossini.\NI'd like to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sir Phederico?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My father just ceded his court rank to me. As so,\NI have full discretion over these negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Negotiations? What exactly\Ndo you think you're going to negotiate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To ensure no more needless bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what this is about, then I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We ask for your assurance\Nfor those who serve the Rossinis
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will not lose their fortunes, nor their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are your demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The entire fortunes\Nof those who serve the Rossinis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also the Crest of Viscount Rossini's family,\Nand the lives of both you and Phederico.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know that my demands\Nare the words of the people in this uprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to take note of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no problem relinquishing my life,\Nand my father's, to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if you were to execute us,\Nand take over as ruler,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that those who pledged loyalty\Nto the Rossinis will remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so I have a proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you allow me to pledge allegiance to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It will be very difficult\Nand time-consuming for you to govern them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But with me at your side,\NI think they'll obey you without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think these terms are unfavorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:20:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To subjugate you for the sole purpose\Nof making my rule go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be a convincing argument\Nfor those who joined in the revolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, I don't wish\Nto annihilate the Rossini family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,During this battle, I realized\Nthat a lot of people are loyal to the Rossinis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to live for their sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound any different\Nthan using me to your advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those are my own words, and my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The most prominent Lord who served the hero,\NJude Cornaro, was a Rossini baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm told that in those days,\Neveryone on this island was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to bring Sistina\Nback to those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To rebuild anew the Sistina\Nof the good old days, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, I'd like to ask you\Nto pledge allegiance to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Sir Phederico will assume responsibility\Nfor what generations of Rossinis have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one thing I can't concede.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, my father\Nis already prepared to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time, the Rossini's way\Nof governing has been reaching its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time,\NI'd lost hope that it could be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But after hearing what you said just now,\NSir Theo, I've changed my way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For Sistina's sake, I'd like to pledge my loyalty\Nto this Lord by the name of Theo Cornaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THE LIBERATOR OF SISTINA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 15\NRETURN
